      "span_text": "Plasma hormones and substrates. The concentrations of individual amino acids from frozen plasma samples obtained at Ϫ15 and 120 min of the infusion were measured with a HPLC method (PICO-TAG reverse-phase column; Waters, Milford, MA) as previously described [CITATION_1] ."
